摩擦游戏可以让你从制作恐怖游戏中抽出时间https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/frictional-games-to-take-time-off-from-making-horror-games-3471605?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=frictional-games-to-take-time-off-from-making-horror-gamesImogen Donovan Fri, 21 Jul 2023 14:09:15 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCPS4PS5 https://www.nme.com/?p=3471605 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我相信这些游戏仍然会让人感觉像是摩擦游戏”</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/frictional-games-to-take-time-off-from-making-horror-games-3471605">摩擦游戏从制作恐怖游戏中抽出时间</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>以<em>《半影》</em>和<em>《失忆症》</em>系列而闻名的瑞典开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/frictional-games">Frictional Games</a>分享了其在未来游戏中淡化恐怖元素的意图。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/sounds-scary-why-horror-game-music-is-the-key-to-unlocking-true-fear-3079713">听起来很可怕：为什么恐怖游戏音乐是解锁真正恐惧的关键</a></strong></li></ul><p>在接受采访时，创意总监 Thomas Grip 解释说，情感投入是 Frictional Games 游戏中最重要的方面，而不是恐惧因素（来自<a href="https://80.lv/articles/frictional-games-on-its-history-developing-horror-games/">80lv</a> ）。 “虽然我们所有的游戏在某种程度上都是恐怖的，但我们真正想做的是获得一种‘可玩的沉浸感’，”他说。 </p><figure id="attachment_3447459" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3447459" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3447459" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker.jpg" alt="失忆症：地堡" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3447459" class="wp-caption-text">失忆症：地堡。图片来源：摩擦游戏</figcaption></figure><p>谈到<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/amnesia-rebirth-is-free-next-week-on-the-epic-games-store-3205766">《失忆症：重生</a></em>》的母性主题和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/soma"><em>SOMA</em></a>关于我们如何定义人类的哲学问题，Grip 赞扬了团队为平衡这些复杂主题以及有趣和恐怖的体验而做出的“整体”努力。</p><p> “我们在恐怖背景下传达了这些主题，但这些故事可以用另一种类型来讲述，”创意总监继续说道。 “对于未来的项目，我认为我们会减少一些恐怖方面的内容，以便更多地关注其他情感品质。”</p><p> “我相信这些游戏仍然会让人感觉像是摩擦游戏。我认为，沉浸感、个人旅程和整体视野是摩擦游戏的定义特征，而不仅仅是恐怖游戏本身，”他总结道。</p><p> Frictional Games 最近发布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/amnesia-the-bunker-trailer-reveals-semi-open-world-ww1-horror-3359772"><em>《失忆症：碉堡》</em></a> ，以第一次世界大战为背景。主角亨利·克莱门特 (Henri Clément) 是一名被怪物困住的士兵，怪物会对玩家在试图逃脱死亡时做出的选择做出反应。据说<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/frictional-is-working-on-a-soma-style-game-alongside-amnesia-the-bunker-3398413">它的下一个标题</a>是一部“更大”的科幻恐怖片，专注于“像你在<em>《SOMA》</em>中看到的那种哲学东西”。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/assassins-creed-syndicate"><em>《刺客信条：枭雄》的</em></a>配音演员维多利亚·阿特金<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/assassins-creed-voice-actor-describes-ai-as-an-invisible-enemy-3471042">表达了她对在 mod 中使用人工智能来模拟演员声音的担忧</a>。</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/frictional-games-to-take-time-off-from-making-horror-games-3471605">摩擦游戏从制作恐怖游戏中抽出时间</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
托尼·贝内特去世，享年 96 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/tony-bennett-dies-ged-96-3471623?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=tony-bennett-dies-ged-96Tom Skinner Fri, 21 Jul 2023 12:51:04 +0000 Music NewsNews..Pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3471623 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2019 年托尼·贝内特的黑白图像" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位标志性歌手于 2016 年被诊断出患有阿尔茨海默氏症</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tony-bennett-dies-aged-96-3471623">托尼·贝内特 (Tony Bennett) 去世，享年 96 岁的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2019 年托尼·贝内特的黑白图像" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/TonyBennett-dies-aged-96-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tony-bennett">，托尼·贝内特</a>去世，享年 96 岁。</p><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2023/music/news/tony-bennett-dead-dies-pop-vocalist-1235676390/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>报道，这位传奇歌手今天早上（7 月 21 日星期五）在纽约去世。</p><p>贝内特于 2016 年被诊断出患有阿尔茨海默氏症。他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tony-bennett-has-been-diagnosed-with-alzheimers-disease-2869644">于 2021 年初公开了自己的病情</a>，但继续录制音乐和现场演唱，直到当年 8 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tony-bennett-retires-from-performing-after-cancelling-remaining-tour-dates-3018434">退役</a>。</p><p>贝内特 1926 年出生于纽约市，在其漫长的职业生涯中赢得了 20 项<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美奖</a>，其中包括终身成就奖。他在全球售出了超过 5000 万张唱片，并以“Rags To Riches”和“I Left My Heart In San Francisco”等热门歌曲而闻名。</p><p>他的首张专辑“Because Of You”于 1952 年发行。Bennett 总共发行了 70 多张专辑。这位资深艺术家的最后一张录音室唱片是 2021 年与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>合作的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tony-bennett-and-lady-gaga-love-for-sale-review-3058264">《Love For Sale》</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3010126" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3010126" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3010126" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/TonyBennettGaga-album.jpg" alt="Lady Gaga 和托尼·贝内特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/TonyBennettGaga-album.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/TonyBennettGaga-album-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/TonyBennettGaga-album-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/TonyBennettGaga-album-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/TonyBennettGaga-album-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/TonyBennettGaga-album-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3010126" class="wp-caption-text"> Lady Gaga 和托尼·贝内特，2021 年。图片来源：凯尔西·贝内特/出版社</figcaption></figure><p>2021 年，贝内特宣布退休前不久，贝内特和 Gaga 在纽约市无线电城音乐厅举办了两场特别演出。这些表演被拍摄成一部名为<em>《最后一次》</em>的电视特别节目，该<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/lady-gaga-tony-bennett-added-last-minute-emmy-nominees-for-concert-special-3282648">特别节目后来获得了艾美奖杰出综艺特别节目类别的提名</a>。</p><p>两人此前曾在 2014 年合作制作了一张名为“Cheek To Cheek”的二重唱唱片。</p><p>在 1965 年接受<em>《生活》杂志</em>采访时，贝内特的朋友、导师和合作者弗兰克·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-sinatra">西纳特拉 (Frank Sinatra)</a>将这位已故明星描述为“业内最好的歌手”（来自<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-11991156" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC 新闻</em></a>）。</p><p> “当我看着他时，他让我兴奋。他让我感动，”西纳特拉解释道。 “他是一位能够理解作曲家想法的歌手，甚至可能更多一些。”</p><p>其他与贝内特合作过的艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aretha-franklin">艾瑞莎·富兰克林</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">埃尔顿·约翰</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-winehouse">艾米·怀恩豪斯</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-michael">乔治·迈克尔</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nile-rodgers">尼罗·罗杰斯（Nile Rodgers）</a>是在社交媒体上向贝内特致敬的人之一。 “我向托尼·贝内特的家人和朋友表示最衷心的哀悼，”他写道。 “他们也是我情感上的家人和朋友。”</p><p>在其他地方，埃尔顿·约翰分享了一张自己与贝内特的照片，并附上信息：“听到托尼去世的消息，我感到非常悲伤。毫无疑问，他是您见过的最优雅的歌手、男人和表演者。</p><p> “他是不可替代的。我爱他、崇拜他。向[妻子]苏珊[克劳]、[儿子兼经理]丹尼和家人表示哀悼。”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我向托尼·贝内特的家人和朋友表示最衷心的哀悼。他们也是我情感上的家人和朋友<a href="https://t.co/eohrA6fpjI">pic.twitter.com/eohrA6fpjI</a></p><p> — 尼罗·罗杰斯 (@nilerodgers) <a href="https://twitter.com/nilerodgers/status/1682377191714091008?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 7 月 21 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-caption